{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradio"]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"struct","roleHeading":"Structure","title":"OUDSRadio","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents9OUDSRadioV","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}]},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely radio, without labels, texts nor icons radios components","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a radio with additional texts and icon, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:isError:)"],"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/body"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/View-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title"